title: Midseason Review + TNF Preview, Stone Cold - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/3
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode as we enter Week 9! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason review the 2021 fantasy season so far! Who can be a fantasy football superstar for the rest of the season? Plus, the Week 9 edition of Buy or Sell, and a preview of Thursday Night Football. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 3rd, 2021.
  
 (05:40) - Buy or Sell
 (12:35) - News & Notes
 (32:05) - Mid-Season Review
 (32:35) - QB Review
 (45:10) - RB Review
 (56:20) - WR Review
 (01:03:05) - TE Review
 (01:06:45) - Thursday Night Breakdown: Jets at Colts
